Personal Insurance
We have options for your home, auto and liability coverage so you're not limited to one plan that may or may not fit your lifestyle.
 



















Personal Insurance








Personal insurance should be just that—personalized. That’s the advantage of using a broker like Higginbotham over insuring directly with a carrier. We have access to multiple insurance carriers for your home, auto, liability, life and medical coverage so you’re not limited to one program that may or may not fit your lifestyle. With our guidance, you’ll be paired with the carriers that offer the best protections for your personal risk factors, tolerance and budget. And when possible, we consolidate your program with fewer carriers to eliminate extraneous costs. It’s the peace of mind that comes from knowing that you have a trusty advisor on your side.



 

 


















