Overview


Higginbotham is a single source for insurance
and financial services that brokers business insurance, employee benefits,
retirement plans, executive benefits, life insurance and home/auto insurance
from more than 250 regional and national carriers. It supplements coverage with
in-house risk management and benefit plan
administration services.


