Fort Worth
























        Who We Are      




Fort Worth is Higginbotham’s birth place and headquarters. Founded in 1948 by Paul C. Higginbotham after returning from World War II, the firm has relocated several times to accommodate its growing staff. In 2001, it moved to its current downtown building, which houses nearly 200 insurance and administrative professionals. It is the center of the firm’s accounting, HR, IT and marketing functions.
But more than our location has changed during the firm’s 60-plus years. What started as a small neighborhood home and auto insurance agency has expanded to one of the largest full-service brokerage firms in Texas and nationwide.
Through experience and growth, we have developed expertise in every area of insurance, employee benefits and risk management—a Single Source solution.
We have successfully ventured beyond Fort Worth to cities throughout Texas. But no matter where you find Higginbotham, our commitment to Single Source solutions is the same.  Paul Higginbotham would be amazed at his legacy.
 

 













