        Higginbotham Insurance Group      

Higginbotham is comprised of offices located across Texas that work in unison to provide a Single Source solution no matter which is your local partner. Each one has the complete insurance and financial service capabilities that differentiate Higginbotham and the personal service that further distinguishes us. Together, we are one of the largest independent insurance brokers in Texas and the U.S.






