									ABOUT HIGGINBOTHAM INSURANCE AGENCY INC
								
HIGGINBOTHAM INSURANCE AGENCY INC has a distinctive partnership with The Hartford1 as an authorized to offer agency for the AARP® Auto and Home Insurance Program from The Hartford in your local area.
The AARP® Auto Insurance Program from The Hartford is specifically designed to reward safer, more experienced drivers with better savings*, a higher level of service, and greater car insurance benefits that include


New Car Replacement §§
Lifetime Renewability †
12 Month Rate Protection


The AARP® Homeowner's Insurance Program from The Hartford is the perfect plan for members who want to protect their home and their possessions. We also offer Condo Insurance and Renters Insurance, with optional Flood and Umbrella insurance.


Full Replacement Cost**
Lifetime Renewability†
"New For Old" Protection of Your Possessions


HIGGINBOTHAM INSURANCE AGENCY INC agents are available to meet with you to offer expert guidance and customized insurance solutions that protect everything you've worked hard for.



