Day Two Services®
We're involved throughout the term of your insurance policy, not just at renewal on day one.
 



















Day Two Services®








No matter what kind of insurance plan you’re looking for, whether it’s for yourself, your business or your employees, Higginbotham can provide options for it. But we don’t stop there. We have in-house subject matter experts providing support after we place your coverage – we call these Day Two Services®. We’re involved throughout the term of your insurance policy, not just at renewal. We even provide an annual service timeline so you know what to expect and when to expect it. Our Day Two Services® encompass everything you need to manage your risks, limit your liability, administer your plans and control your costs.
 


















