Business Insurance
We develop a custom marketing and coverage plan after getting to know your business goals and exposures.
 



















Business Insurance








We don’t assume that the insurance coverage you’ve had in place meets your needs today or that it will tomorrow. Instead, we design a custom coverage plan based on our assessment of your unique exposures. Then we market those exposures to appropriately place your coverage with our highly rated insurance carriers and get the best value for the price you pay.
Lots of insurance brokers can provide coverage for your business. Higginbotham provides that and much more. We deliver a detailed market analysis with side-by-side quotes and all the data you need to make an informed carrier selection and avoid rushed decision-making. Once coverage is placed, we develop an annual service timeline to track pivotal account and risk management activities to demonstrate how we will fulfill our service commitments to you throughout the coverage term.
 



 

 


















